doctype html
html
	head
		meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
		title Eska - Simple chat app
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/frontpage.css')
	body: #top
		.top-bar-container(data-sticky-container)
			.sticky(data-sticky data-options="anchor: page; marginTop: 0; stickyOn: small;")
				.top-bar
					.title-area.top-bar-title
						.menu-text.name Eska's chat app
						span.menu-toggle(data-responsive-toggle="responsive-menu" data-hide-for="medium") Menu 
							button.menu-icon(type='button' data-toggle)
					#responsive-menu
						.top-bar-right
							.menu.align-right
								li(role='menuitem'): a(href='#top'): h5 Home
								li(role='menuitem'): a(href='#about'): h5 About

		section.jumbo
			.row
				.columns.large-12.small-12.medium-12
					h1.text-center Simple Chat app
			.row.align-center
					.columns.small-12.large-5.medium-8
						.input-group
							input#user-name(type="text", placeholder='Type inn you\'r name...')
							.input-group-field
							input#submit.button(type='submit' value='Join chat!')


		section#about
			.row
				.columns
					.text-center
						h2 About this project
						p The purpose of this project is to learn react, foundation and socket.io. The site is built with gulp, and served as an express application. I thought jade might would be usefull, untill I understood that I was supposed to write html inside the react render function. The jade template became pretty small because of that, and the only thing the body contains is a #chat-app tag, hmm... not quite as planned. The site is still under development. I'm also going to test out the cool new library motion ui in this project.

					.row
						.columns.large-4.small-12.medium-4
							h3.text-center GitHub project
							a(href='https://github.com/Eskalol/simpleChatApp'): img(src='imgs/GitHub-Mark.png')
							p Here is a link to the git project, I don't maintain the app often, maybe if theres some crucial bugs.
								br
								a(href='https://github.com/Eskalol/simpleChatApp') Github: Eskalol
						.columns.large-4.small-12.medium-4
							h3.text-center Yeoman
							img(src='imgs/yeoman-logo.png')
							p There will be a yeomam generator soon...
						.columns.large-4.small-12.medium-4
							h3.text-center Heroku
							a(href='www.heroku.com'): img(src='imgs/heroku-logo-for-facebook.png')
							p This project is hosted on heroku, I usually host my test projects there, really cool though. check it out :)
		

		footer#footer.footer
			.row.fullWidth
				.small-12.medium-3.large-4.columns
					i.fi-mail
					p.text-center.contact contact: eskil.nordland@gmail.com


		script(src="js/vendor.js")
		script(src="js/app.js")